Download TIGER shapes for Estates (US Virgin Islands)

Source: R/estates.R
tt_estates.Rd

Download TIGER shapes for Estates (US Virgin Islands)

Usage

tt_estates(year = 2021)

Arguments

year

Integer year. Required. Years < 2012 are not currently supported.

Value

sf data.frame

Examples

tt_estates()
